Class TracingSymbolProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • software.amazon.smithy.codegen.core.trace.TracingSymbolProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SymbolProvider
    public final class TracingSymbolProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements SymbolProvider
    Decorates a SymbolProvider with a TraceFile.Builder and adds a ShapeLink object to the builder on each call to toSymbol.
